Title: Golden Bat Cigerettes
DateModified: '2019-02-25'
DatePublished: '2019-02-25'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/golden-bat-cigerettes
SetInCountry: Japan
Category: I didn't expect to find
AuthorName: Ermelinda Reece
AuthorCountry: United States of America
Text: Golden Bat Cigarettes dives into an uncovering the history of her grandfather's
  time in Okinawa following World War Two. The story is set over the course of 12
  days between various parts of Japan. She soon begins to  uncover more information
  and yet more answers as she meets various characters that played a part in her grandfather's
  experience. Unknown stories,secrets and barriers are crossed and she finds herself
  questioning her own understanding of the man she called her grandfather as well
  her understanding of the various sacrifices made throughout her family history.
